  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>We are a stainless steel stockist located in the northern part of Singapore, expanding our stainless steel business across Singapore and the Asia region.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Drive business growth by developing new customers and executing strategic sales plans to expand our stainless steel market presence in Singapore and Asia.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Achieve targeted sales growth by executing effective sales strategies within the stainless steel market</li><li>Develop and secure new customer accounts to expand the company’s market reach</li><li>Design and implement a strategic business plan that broadens the customer base and strengthens market presence</li><li>Build and maintain strong, long-lasting customer relationships by understanding client needs and delivering tailored solutions</li><li>Present detailed sales, revenue, and expense reports along with realistic sales forecasts to the management team</li><li>Identify emerging markets and monitor market shifts by analyzing new products and competitor activities to inform sales strategies</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in business administration or a related field</li><li>Proven track record as a sales representative or sales manager with consistent achievement or surpassing of sales targets</li><li>Demonstrated ability to drive the sales process from planning through to closing deals</li><li>Strong business acumen and industry knowledge relevant to stainless steel markets</li></ul>",
